item.title: EXPANSION V8.7.5 1.50 ATS
item.description:
EXPANSION V8.7.5 1.50 ATS

Changelog v8.7.5 – Fix US 34 west of McCook NE, thanks sickrun

This version has all 3 required files combined into 1 file. There have been additions and fixes. This version is ONLY for 1.50, do not use in 1.49. Roughly 60 loading/unloading locations updated for 1.50, still more than 100 to do. Nebraska is required as are all SCS state DLC’s,


How to install ETS2 mods or ATS Mods

In Euro Truck Simulator 2 it’s easy to install mods. You just need to download mod from here, copy/unzip files into: “My Documents\Euro Truck Simulator 2\mod” folder or if you play ATS please install mods to: “My Documents\American Truck Simulator\mod” folder. To unzip files you can use: WinRAR or 7zip. After that you need to activate the mods you want to use.

item.title: Set of toys & Air Fresheners for the Interior of Trucks v1.50 ATS
item.description:
Set of toys & Air Fresheners for the Interior of Trucks v1.50 ATS

This mod includes a selection of Air Fresheners & hanging toys for all SCS trucks. This mod also supports GTM 610, t800, w900b, and 567. 12 State Seals representing the 12 States in game. There are several classic tree fresheners. Some DC characters. Deadpool. A middle finger for the mod theives who will steal this (sites listed on finger) and upload it to their sites, and some Stig things. A Collections of Star Trek insignia. Four Orville group badges. New Mexico symbol.
